  +-FunctionCall(GoogleSQL:$greater(INT64, INT64) -> BOOL)
    +-FunctionCall(sample_functions:deprecation_warning() -> INT64)
    +-FunctionCall(sample_functions:deprecation_warning() -> INT64)


DEPRECATION WARNING:
